Run shell and Python code in a sandbox with generated maco tools.

Generated MCP tools are importable as:
  from tools.<server> import <tool>

{% include "server_catalog.j2" %}

Inspect generated tool code inside the sandbox at:
  {{ wrapper_root }}/<server>/__init__.py
  {{ wrapper_root }}/<server>/<tool>.py

Use bash for discovery with rg/fd:
  rg --files {{ wrapper_root }}
  fd . {{ wrapper_root }} -t f
  rg "^def " {{ wrapper_root }}/<server>

Use code_execute to run Python scripts that import generated tools.
